00046 void strsmKernel(const real *pA, real *pB, real *pC, real *pBHat, const int k, const int stepC, const int flagisN, const int flagisL)
00047 {
00048   __float2_t sum0, sum1, sum2, sum3, sum4, sum5, sum6, sum7;
00049   __float2_t sum8, sum9, suma, sumb, sumc, sumd, sume, sumf;
00050   __float2_t * restrict ptrB     = (__float2_t *) pB;
00051   __float2_t * restrict ptrA     = (__float2_t *) pA;
00052   __float2_t * restrict ptrC;
00053   __float2_t regC, regS, regS0, regS1, regS2, regS3;
00054   real reg0, reg1, * restrict pRegB;
00055   __float2_t * restrict ptrBH;
00056   const real * restrict pReg;
00057   int_least16_t index;
00058 
00059   // zero out accumulators
00060   sum0 = 0.0;
00061   sum1 = 0.0;
00062   sum2 = 0.0;
00063   sum3 = 0.0;
00064   sum4 = 0.0;
00065   sum5 = 0.0;
00066   sum6 = 0.0;
00067   sum7 = 0.0;
00068   sum8 = 0.0;
00069   sum9 = 0.0;
00070   suma = 0.0;

00073   sumd = 0.0;
00074   sume = 0.0;
00075   sumf = 0.0;

00077   for (index = 0; index < k; index++)
00078   { // loop over k;
00079     // each iteration performs rank one update of 4x1 by 1x8
00080     // matrices of A and B respectively; result is
00081     // accumulated over 4x8 matrix
00082         __float2_t b01, b23, b45, b67, a01, a23;
00083         __x128_t   reg128;
00084 
00085     a01 = *ptrA++;
00086         a23 = *ptrA++;
00087 
00088     b01 = *ptrB++;
00089     b23 = *ptrB++;
00090     b45 = *ptrB++;
00091     b67 = *ptrB++;
00092 
00093     reg128 = _cmpysp(a01, b01);
00094     // accumulate a[0]*b[1] and -a[0]*b[0]
00095     sum0 = _daddsp(sum0, _lof2_128(reg128));
00096     // accumulate a[1]*b[0] and a[1]*b[1]
00097     sum1 = _daddsp(sum1, _hif2_128(reg128));
00098 
00099     reg128 = _cmpysp(a01, b23);
00100     // accumulate a[0]*b[3] and -a[0]*b[2]
00101     sum2 = _daddsp(sum2, _lof2_128(reg128));
00102     // accumulate a[1]*b[2] and a[1]*b[3]
00103     sum3 = _daddsp(sum3, _hif2_128(reg128));
00104 
00105     reg128 = _cmpysp(a01, b45);
00106     // accumulate a[0]*b[5] and -a[0]*b[4]
00107     sum4 = _daddsp(sum4, _lof2_128(reg128));
00108     // accumulate a[1]*b[4] and a[1]*b[5]
00109     sum5 = _daddsp(sum5, _hif2_128(reg128));
00110 
00111     reg128 = _cmpysp(a01, b67);
00112     // accumulate a[0]*b[7] and -a[0]*b[6]
00113     sum6 = _daddsp(sum6, _lof2_128(reg128));
00114     // accumulate a[1]*b[6] and a[1]*b[7]
00115     sum7 = _daddsp(sum7, _hif2_128(reg128));
00116 
00117     reg128 = _cmpysp(a23, b01);
00118     // accumulate a[2]*b[1] and -a[2]*b[0]
00119     sum8 = _daddsp(sum8, _lof2_128(reg128));
00120     // accumulate a[3]*b[0] and a[3]*b[1]
00121     sum9 = _daddsp(sum9, _hif2_128(reg128));
00122 
00123     reg128 = _cmpysp(a23, b23);
00124     // accumulate a[2]*b[3] and -a[2]*b[2]
00125     suma = _daddsp(suma, _lof2_128(reg128));
00126     // accumulate a[3]*b[2] and a[3]*b[3]
00127     sumb = _daddsp(sumb, _hif2_128(reg128));
00128 
00129     reg128 = _cmpysp(a23, b45);
00130     // accumulate a[2]*b[5] and -a[2]*b[4]
00131     sumc = _daddsp(sumc, _lof2_128(reg128));
00132     // accumulate a[3]*b[4] and a[3]*b[5]
00133     sumd = _daddsp(sumd, _hif2_128(reg128));
00134 
00135     reg128 = _cmpysp(a23, b67);
00136     // accumulate a[2]*b[7] and -a[2]*b[6]
00137     sume = _daddsp(sume, _lof2_128(reg128));
00138     // accumulate a[3]*b[6] and a[3]*b[7]
00139     sumf = _daddsp(sumf, _hif2_128(reg128));
00140 
00141   }

00143   if(flagisN>0) // saving in normal form
00144   {
00145         if(flagisL)
00146         {
00147           index = (stepC>>1)-2;
00148

00150           // c[0,1] and c[1,1]

00152           // c[0,0] and c[1,0]

00156           // c[0,3] and c[1,3]

00272           // update c[2,0] and c[3,0]
